1. Introduction

In today’s digital age, technology plays a vital role in education, communication, and professional growth. Digital literacy is the ability to use digital tools effectively, responsibly, and safely.

This project was assigned to enhance our understanding of digital platforms, online communication, and cyber safety. As a Student Digital Ambassador, my role is to guide peers in navigating the digital world responsibly.

This portfolio includes five tasks that demonstrate my learning and practical application of digital literacy skills.

2. Objective of the Project

The main objectives of this project are:

To understand the concept of digital literacy
To develop a professional digital identity
To learn effective online communication
To explore useful digital platforms
To create awareness about cybercrime and online safety
