7. Task 5: Cybercrime Awareness

This task focused on understanding cybercrime and prevention methods.

Case Study:

A student received a phishing email requesting bank details. The email appeared genuine, and the student shared sensitive information, resulting in financial loss.

Prevention Measures:
Avoid clicking unknown links
Verify sender identity
Use strong passwords
Enable two-factor authentication
Keep software updated
Learning Outcome:

I understood the risks of cybercrime and how to protect myself and others online.

